== 截角多面體或更高維的圖形 ==
[[File:Birectified_cube_sequence.png|thumb]]
當截角一詞被用在正多面體或正鑲嵌圖上時，通常代表「[[#均勻截角|'''均勻截角''']]」<ref name="N.W. Johnson 1966">N.W. Johnson: ''The Theory of Uniform Polytopes and Honeycombs'', Ph.D. Dissertation, University of Toronto, 1966</ref>，其通常代表截角截至所有面都是正多邊形的深度。
:[[Image:Cube_truncation_sequence.svg|320px]]
上表則展示了立方體透過截角深度不斷加深的截角變換將立方體變換為截角立方體和截半立方體的過程。

若[[原像_(幾何)|原像 (幾何)]]在[[施萊夫利符號|施萊夫利符號]]中計為{''p'',''q'',...}，則在上圖表中間的紫色截角結果可以記為'''t'''{''p'',''q'',...}<ref name="Arthur Sherk 1995">''[http://www.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-0471010030.html Kaleidoscopes: Selected Writings of H.S.M. Coxeter] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-0471010030.html |date=20160711140441 }}'', edited by F. Arthur Sherk, Peter McMullen, Anthony C. Thompson, Asia Ivic Weiss, Wiley-Interscience Publication, 1995, {{isbn|978-0-471-01003-6}}</ref>。而截半為截角截到原本的稜消失，因此截半也稱為完全截角<ref name="Zofia Grabowieck 2019">{{cite journal | author=Zofia Grabowieck | title=The decoration of a Coxeter–Dynkin diagram andthe Schl ̈afli symbol as two methods to describepolytopes generated by finite reflection groups | volume=1194|year=2019 | doi=10.1088/1742-6596/1194/1/012039 | journal = Journal of Physics: Conference Series}}</ref>。

繼續更深入地截角同樣可以產生被截之面為正多邊形面的均勻截角形式。比截半再更深入的均勻截角形式為過截角。過截角的效果為移除多面體面的所有邊，但有保留部分多面體原有面的內部之局部。截角八面體則為立方體套用過截角變換後的像。<ref name="book diudea2017multi">{{Cite book
  |title=Multi-shell Polyhedral Clusters
  |author=Diudea, M.V.
  |isbn=9783319641232
  |series=Carbon Materials: Chemistry and Physics
  |year=2017
  |page=26
  |publisher=Springer International Publishing}}</ref>

過截角同樣也存在完全截角的形式，即完全過截角，又稱為過截半或雙截半。其效果為截角截到原有面消失的深度<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.maths.qmul.ac.uk/~whitty/LSBU/MathsStudyGroup/ADFnotes-Regular-polytopes.pdf | publisher=maths.qmul.ac.uk | title=Regular polytopes | author=Tony Forbes | date=December 2014 | access-date=2019-10-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008123905/http://www.maths.qmul.ac.uk/~whitty/LSBU/MathsStudyGroup/ADFnotes-Regular-polytopes.pdf | archive-date=2018-10-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。大部分的三維圖形經過'''過截半'''變換後會轉變為對偶多面體，例如[[正八面體|正八面體]]為立方體過截半的結果，在施萊夫利符號中可以用2r{4,3}表示。

