== 裁邊 ==
{{Main|倒角 (幾何)}}
'''裁邊'''又稱'''截邊'''、'''裁稜'''或'''截稜'''是一種與截角類似的操作，其為將一個幾何結構的所有稜或邊切去。裁邊在三維空間中稱為倒角，其結果為將多面體的所有稜替換成六邊形面<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://bendwavy.org/klitzing/incmats/cube-trunc-rad.htm | title=cube-trunc-rad, Polytopes & their Incidence Matrices | publisher=bendwavy.org | author=Dr. Richard Klitzing | access-date=2019-11-05 | archive-date=2019-11-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105070836/https://bendwavy.org/klitzing/incmats/cube-trunc-rad.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在四維空間中則會使幾何結構的所有稜被替換為[[雙角錐柱|雙角錐柱]]形狀的胞。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/38db/f0a694adcd54c4845eeebccbfb0143ab6fb8.pdf | title=Crystallization in systems of hard polyhedra | publisher=semanticscholar.org | author=Richmond S. Newman | access-date=2019-11-05 | archive-date=2019-11-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105071417/https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/38db/f0a694adcd54c4845eeebccbfb0143ab6fb8.pdf | dead-url=yes }}</ref>
